name: UH (UntitledMind)
description:
Keep Moving. Don't die. EVER.

HOW TO PLAY

Don't touch anything that appears, or you will die.

CONTROLS

Moving Foward / Moving Backward - W / Up Key / S / Down Key

Turning - A / Left Key / D / Right Key

Invincibility - Space (Cooldown - 8 Seconds)

UH

It's all I can think anymore.
